lessons.title: Python l g?
lessons.content_text:
Gii thiu v Python

Python l mt ngn ng lp trnh bc cao, c thit k vi trit l nhn mnh kh nng c code. C php n gin ca Python cho php lp trnh vin din t cc khi nim trong t dng code hn so vi cc ngn ng nh C++ hoc Java.

Ti sao hc Python?

  • D hc: C php r rng, gn vi ngn ng t nhin
  • a nng: Web, AI, Data Science, Automation
  • Cng ng ln: Nhiu ti liu v th vin
  • Nhu cu cao: c nhiu cng ty s dng

ng dng ca Python

Python c s dng rng ri trong nhiu lnh vc:

  1. Pht trin web (Django, Flask)
  2. Khoa hc d liu (Pandas, NumPy)
  3. Machine Learning (TensorFlow, PyTorch)
  4. T ng ha v scripting

lessons.title: Ci t Python
lessons.content_text:
Hng dn ci t Python

Windows

  1. Truy cp python.org
  2. Ti phin bn Python mi nht
  3. Chy installer v chn Add Python to PATH
  4. Nhn Install Now

Kim tra ci t

python --version

Nu hin th phin bn Python, bn ci t thnh cng!

IDE khuyn dng

  • VS Code: Min ph, nh, nhiu extension
  • PyCharm: Chuyn nghip cho Python
  • Jupyter Notebook: Tt cho Data Science

Th nghim

lessons.title: Bin trong Python
lessons.content_text:
Bin l g?

Bin l ni lu tr d liu trong chng trnh. Trong Python, bn khng cn khai bo kiu d liu.

Cch to bin

age = 25
height = 1.65
is_student = True

Quy tc t tn bin

  • Bt u bng ch ci hoc du gch di
  • Ch cha ch ci, s v du gch di
  • Phn bit ch hoa ch thng
  • Khng dng t kha Python

lessons.title: Kiu d liu c bn
lessons.content_text:
Cc kiu d liu trong Python

1. S nguyn (int)

lessons.title: JSX v Components
lessons.content_text:
JSX - JavaScript XML

JSX cho php vit HTML trong JavaScript.

const element = <h1>Hello, world!</h1>;

Function Component

function Welcome(props) {
  return <h1>Hello, {props.name}</h1>;
}

Props

Props l cch truyn d liu t component cha xung component con.

Quy tc JSX

  • Phi c mt element gc bao bc
  • ng tt c cc tags
  • Dng camelCase cho attributes

lessons.title: Machine Learning l g?
lessons.content_text:
Gii thiu Machine Learning

Machine Learning (ML) l mt nhnh ca Tr tu nhn to (AI), cho php my tnh hc t d liu m khng cn lp trnh tng minh.

Cc loi Machine Learning

  • Supervised Learning: Hc c gim st vi d liu c nhn
  • Unsupervised Learning: Hc khng gim st, tm patterns trong d liu
  • Reinforcement Learning: Hc tng cng qua tng tc vi mi trng

ng dng thc t

ML c ng dng trong recommendation systems, fraud detection, medical diagnosis, autonomous vehicles...

lessons.title: Quy trnh xy dng m hnh ML
lessons.content_text:
ML Pipeline

Mt d n ML in hnh bao gm cc bc:

  1. Data Collection: Thu thp d liu t cc ngun
  2. Data Preprocessing: Lm sch, x l missing values, encoding
  3. Feature Engineering: To v chn features quan trng
  4. Model Selection: Chn thut ton ph hp
  5. Training: Hun luyn m hnh trn training set
  6. Evaluation: nh gi trn validation/test set
  7. Deployment: Trin khai m hnh vo production

lessons.title: Linear v Logistic Regression
lessons.content_text:
Regression Algorithms

Linear Regression

D on gi tr lin tc bng cch tm ng thng tt nht: y = wx + b

from sklearn.linear_model import LinearRegression\nmodel = LinearRegression()\nmodel.fit(X_train, y_train)

Logistic Regression

Phn loi binary s dng sigmoid function: (z) = 1/(1+e^-z)

Output l xc sut thuc class positive.

lessons.title: Decision Trees v Random Forest
lessons.content_text:
Tree-based Methods

Decision Tree

Thut ton phn loi/hi quy da trn cy quyt nh. S dng Information Gain hoc Gini Impurity split.

Random Forest

Ensemble ca nhiu decision trees:

  • Bagging: Training trn random subsets
  • Feature randomness: Chn random features ti mi split
  • Voting: Kt hp kt qu t nhiu trees

u im: Gim overfitting, robust vi outliers.

lessons.title: K-Means Clustering
lessons.content_text:
Clustering vi K-Means

K-Means l thut ton clustering ph bin nht:

Thut ton

  1. Chn K centroids ngu nhin
  2. Gn mi im vo cluster gn nht
  3. Cp nht centroid = mean ca cluster
  4. Lp li n khi hi t

Chn K ti u

  • Elbow Method
  • Silhouette Score

lessons.title: Model Evaluation Metrics
lessons.content_text:
nh gi m hnh ML

Classification Metrics

  • Accuracy: (TP+TN)/(TP+TN+FP+FN)
  • Precision: TP/(TP+FP)
  • Recall: TP/(TP+FN)
  • F1-Score: 2*(Precision*Recall)/(Precision+Recall)
  • AUC-ROC: Area under ROC curve

Regression Metrics

  • MAE, MSE, RMSE, R

lessons.content_text:
Python cho Data Science

lessons.content_text:

Jupyter Notebook

Interactive computing environment cho data analysis:

  • Kt hp code, text, v visualizations

Virtual Environment

lessons.title: NumPy Arrays v Operations
lessons.content_text:
NumPy Fundamentals

Creating Arrays

import numpy as np

arr = np.array([1, 2, 3])
matrix = np.zeros((3, 3))
random = np.random.randn(100)

Array Operations

# Vectorized operations
arr * 2
arr + arr
np.dot(matrix1, matrix2)

NumPy nhanh hn Python lists 10-100x nh optimized C code.

lessons.title: Pandas DataFrame Mastery
lessons.content_text:
Pandas cho Data Analysis

DataFrame Basics

import pandas as pd

df = pd.read_csv("data.csv")
df.head()
df.describe()
df.info()

Data Manipulation

# Filtering
df[df["age"] > 25]

# Groupby
df.groupby("category").mean()

# Merge
pd.merge(df1, df2, on="id")

lessons.title: Matplotlib v Seaborn
lessons.content_text:
Data Visualization

Matplotlib

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
plt.plot(x, y)
plt.xlabel("X axis")
plt.title("My Plot")
plt.show()

Seaborn

import seaborn as sns

sns.heatmap(correlation_matrix)
sns.boxplot(x="category", y="value", data=df)
sns.pairplot(df)

lessons.content_text:
Plotly cho Interactive Charts

fig = px.scatter(df, x="gdp", y="life_exp",
                 size="population",
                 color="continent",
                 hover_name="country",
                 animation_frame="year")

Dashboard vi Dash

Plotly Dash cho php to web dashboards tng tc vi Python.

lessons.title: Perceptron v Neural Network
lessons.content_text:
Neural Networks c bn

Perceptron

n v c bn ca neural network: y = f((wi*xi) + b)

Multi-layer Perceptron

  • Input layer: Nhn d liu u vo
  • Hidden layers: Hc representations
  • Output layer: a ra d on

Activation Functions

ReLU: max(0, x), Sigmoid: 1/(1+e^-x), Tanh: (e^x - e^-x)/(e^x + e^-x)

lessons.title: Backpropagation v Optimization
lessons.content_text:
Training Neural Networks

Backpropagation

Thut ton tnh gradient cp nht weights:

  1. Forward pass: Tnh output
  2. Compute loss: L(y, )
  3. Backward pass: Tnh L/w
  4. Update: w = w - * L/w

Optimizers

  • SGD, Momentum
  • Adam, RMSprop

lessons.title: CNN Architecture
lessons.content_text:
Convolutional Neural Networks

Convolution Layer

p dng filters detect features: edges, textures, shapes...

Key Components

  • Convolution: Feature extraction
  • Pooling: Downsampling (Max, Average)
  • Flatten + FC: Classification

Famous Architectures

LeNet, AlexNet, VGG, ResNet, EfficientNet

lessons.title: Transfer Learning
lessons.content_text:
Transfer Learning

S dng pre-trained models gii quyt bi ton mi:

from tensorflow.keras.applications import ResNet50

base_model = ResNet50(weights="imagenet", include_top=False)
base_model.trainable = False

model = Sequential([
    base_model,
    GlobalAveragePooling2D(),
    Dense(num_classes, activation="softmax")
])

u im: t data, train nhanh, performance tt.

lessons.title: Object Detection vi YOLO
lessons.content_text:
Object Detection

YOLO (You Only Look Once)

Real-time object detection:

  • Chia image thnh grid cells
  • Mi cell predict bounding boxes v class probabilities
  • Non-max suppression loi b duplicates

Versions

YOLOv3, YOLOv5, YOLOv8 - ngy cng nhanh v chnh xc hn.

lessons.title: Image Segmentation
lessons.content_text:
Semantic Segmentation

Phn loi tng pixel trong image:

Architectures

  • FCN: Fully Convolutional Networks
  • U-Net: Encoder-Decoder vi skip connections
  • DeepLab: Atrous convolution

Instance Segmentation

Mask R-CNN: Kt hp detection + segmentation

lessons.title: Big Data v 5Vs
lessons.content_text:
Gii thiu Big Data

5Vs of Big Data

  • Volume: Lng d liu khng l (TB, PB)
  • Velocity: Tc sinh data cao
  • Variety: a dng format (structured, unstructured)
  • Veracity: tin cy ca data
  • Value: Gi tr business t data

lessons.title: Kin trc Big Data
lessons.content_text:
Big Data Architecture

Lambda Architecture

  • Batch Layer: Process historical data
  • Speed Layer: Real-time processing
  • Serving Layer: Query results

Kappa Architecture

Simplified: Ch dng stream processing cho c batch v real-time.

lessons.title: HDFS v MapReduce
lessons.content_text:
Hadoop Core

HDFS

Distributed File System:

  • NameNode: Metadata management
  • DataNode: Store data blocks
  • Replication: Fault tolerance

MapReduce

// Map: (key, value) -> list(key2, value2)\n// Reduce: (key2, list(value2)) -> list(value3)

lessons.title: Hive v HBase
lessons.content_text:
Hadoop Ecosystem

Apache Hive

SQL interface cho Hadoop:

CREATE TABLE users (
  id INT,
  name STRING
) STORED AS PARQUET;

SELECT * FROM users WHERE age > 25;

Apache HBase

NoSQL database trn HDFS cho random read/write access.

lessons.title: Apache Spark Core
lessons.content_text:
Apache Spark

RDD (Resilient Distributed Dataset)

from pyspark import SparkContext

sc = SparkContext()
rdd = sc.textFile("data.txt")
words = rdd.flatMap(lambda x: x.split())
counts = words.countByValue()

u im so vi MapReduce

In-memory processing, 100x faster, rich APIs.

lessons.title: Spark SQL v MLlib
lessons.content_text:
Spark Advanced

Spark SQL

from pyspark.sql import SparkSession

spark = SparkSession.builder.getOrCreate()
df = spark.read.parquet("data.parquet")
df.createOrReplaceTempView("data")
spark.sql("SELECT * FROM data").show()

MLlib

Distributed ML: Classification, Regression, Clustering, Collaborative Filtering.

lessons.title: Knowledge-based Systems
lessons.content_text:
Expert Systems

Thnh phn

  • Knowledge Base: Facts v Rules
  • Inference Engine: Suy lun logic
  • User Interface: Giao tip vi ngi dng

Knowledge Representation

IF-THEN rules, Semantic networks, Frames, Ontologies

lessons.title: Inference v Reasoning
lessons.content_text:
Suy lun trong Expert Systems

Forward Chaining

Data-driven: T facts conclusions

Backward Chaining

Goal-driven: T goal find supporting facts

V d

Rule: IF fever AND cough THEN flu\nFact: fever = true, cough = true\nConclusion: flu = true

lessons.title: Fuzzy Sets v Membership Functions
lessons.content_text:
Fuzzy Logic

Fuzzy vs Crisp

Classical logic: TRUE/FALSE. Fuzzy: Degree of truth [0, 1]

Membership Functions

  • Triangular
  • Trapezoidal
  • Gaussian

V d: "Nhit cao" vi (35C) = 0.8

lessons.title: Fuzzy Inference Systems
lessons.content_text:
Fuzzy Control

Quy trnh

  1. Fuzzification: Crisp Fuzzy
  2. Rule Evaluation: Apply fuzzy rules
  3. Aggregation: Combine rule outputs
  4. Defuzzification: Fuzzy Crisp

ng dng

iu khin my git, camera autofocus, ABS brakes...

lessons.title: Agent Architecture
lessons.content_text:
Intelligent Agents

nh ngha

Agent: Thc th t tr, perceive environment v take actions

Agent Types

  • Simple Reflex Agent
  • Model-based Agent
  • Goal-based Agent
  • Utility-based Agent
  • Learning Agent

lessons.title: Multi-Agent Coordination
lessons.content_text:
Multi-Agent Systems

Communication

FIPA ACL: Request, Inform, Propose, Accept...

Coordination Mechanisms

  • Auction-based
  • Negotiation

ng dng

Swarm robotics, traffic control, supply chain optimization

lessons.title: Text Preprocessing
lessons.content_text:
NLP Pipeline c bn

Text Cleaning

import re
text = re.sub(r"[^a-zA-Z]", " ", text)
text = text.lower()

Tokenization

from nltk.tokenize import word_tokenize
tokens = word_tokenize("Hello world!")
# ["Hello", "world", "!"]

lessons.title: Stemming v Lemmatization
lessons.content_text:
Word Normalization

Stemming

from nltk.stem import PorterStemmer
ps = PorterStemmer()
ps.stem("running") # "run"

Lemmatization

from nltk.stem import WordNetLemmatizer
lemmatizer = WordNetLemmatizer()
lemmatizer.lemmatize("better", pos="a") # "good"

Lemmatization chnh xc hn nhng chm hn Stemming.

lessons.title: Word Embeddings
lessons.content_text:
Word Representations

One-hot Encoding

Sparse, no semantic meaning

Word2Vec

  • CBOW: Predict word from context
  • Skip-gram: Predict context from word
from gensim.models import Word2Vec\nmodel = Word2Vec(sentences, vector_size=100)\nmodel.wv.most_similar("king")

GloVe

Global Vectors: Co-occurrence matrix factorization

lessons.title: RNN v LSTM
lessons.content_text:
Sequence Models

RNN

Recurrent Neural Network: ht = f(ht-1, xt)

Vn : Vanishing gradient

LSTM

Long Short-Term Memory vi gates:

  • Forget gate: Qun thng tin c
  • Input gate: Thm thng tin mi
  • Output gate: Xut hidden state

lessons.title: Attention v Transformers
lessons.content_text:
Transformer Architecture

Self-Attention

Attention(Q,K,V) = softmax(QK^T/dk)V

Transformer Components

  • Multi-head Attention
  • Positional Encoding
  • Feed-forward layers
  • Layer Normalization

"Attention is All You Need" (2017) - Vaswani et al.

lessons.title: BERT v GPT
lessons.content_text:
Pre-trained Language Models

BERT

Bidirectional Encoder: Masked LM + Next Sentence Prediction

from transformers import BertTokenizer, BertModel\ntokenizer = BertTokenizer.from_pretrained("bert-base-uncased")\nmodel = BertModel.from_pretrained("bert-base-uncased")

GPT

Generative Pre-trained Transformer: Autoregressive LM

GPT-3, GPT-4: Few-shot learning capabilities

lessons.title: KDD Process
lessons.content_text:
Knowledge Discovery in Databases

KDD Steps

  1. Selection: Chn relevant data
  2. Preprocessing: Cleaning, handling missing values
  3. Transformation: Feature engineering, normalization
  4. Data Mining: Apply algorithms
  5. Interpretation: Evaluate v visualize patterns

lessons.title: Data Preprocessing
lessons.content_text:
Preprocessing Techniques

Missing Values

  • Deletion: Remove rows/columns
  • Imputation: Mean, median, mode, KNN

Outlier Detection

  • Z-score method
  • IQR method
  • Isolation Forest

Feature Scaling

Min-max normalization, Standardization (Z-score)

lessons.title: Association Rules Mining
lessons.content_text:
Frequent Pattern Mining

Concepts

  • Support: P(A B)
  • Confidence: P(B|A)
  • Lift: P(B|A)/P(B)

Apriori Algorithm

Generate frequent itemsets Generate rules

from mlxtend.frequent_patterns import apriori\nfrequent_items = apriori(df, min_support=0.1)

lessons.title: FP-Growth Algorithm
lessons.content_text:
FP-Growth

Faster than Apriori: No candidate generation

Steps

  1. Build FP-tree t transactions
  2. Mine patterns t FP-tree

u im

  • Ch 2 ln scan database
  • Compress data vo FP-tree
  • No candidate generation

lessons.title: Classification Algorithms
lessons.content_text:
Classification trong Data Mining

Decision Tree

ID3, C4.5, CART - da trn Information Gain, Gini Index

Naive Bayes

P(C|X) P(C) * P(xi|C)

SVM

Find hyperplane vi maximum margin

Ensemble Methods

Bagging, Boosting (AdaBoost, XGBoost)

lessons.title: Clustering Techniques
lessons.content_text:
Clustering Methods

Partitioning

  • K-Means, K-Medoids

Hierarchical

  • Agglomerative (bottom-up)
  • Divisive (top-down)
  • Dendrograms

Density-based

  • DBSCAN: Core points, border points, noise

Model-based

  • Gaussian Mixture Models (GMM)

questions.explanation: Files Python c phn m rng .py

questions.question_text: Kiu d liu no sau y KHNG c trong Python?
questions.explanation: Python khng c kiu char ring bit, chui 1 k t vn l str.

questions.question_text: Kt qu ca type(3.14) l g?
questions.explanation: 3.14 l s thc, c kiu float trong Python.

questions.question_text: Trong Python, bin phn bit ch hoa ch thng?
questions.explanation: Python phn bit ch hoa/thng: name v Name l hai bin khc nhau.

Hc t d liu khng c nhn
Hc thng qua th v sai

questions.explanation: K-Means l thut ton clustering thuc Unsupervised Learning.

questions.explanation: Overfitting l khi m hnh hc thuc training data v khng tng qut ha tt.

questions.question_text: React c pht trin bi cng ty no?
questions.explanation: React c pht trin v duy tr bi Facebook (nay l Meta).

questions.question_text: JSX l vit tt ca g?
questions.explanation: JSX = JavaScript XML, cho php vit HTML-like syntax trong JavaScript.

questions.question_text: Props trong React c th thay i (mutable)?
questions.explanation: Props l immutable, ch c truyn t cha sang con v khng th thay i bi component nhn.

questions.question_text: Hook no dng  qun l state trong Function Component?
questions.explanation: useState l hook c bn nht  qun l local state trong function component.

questions.question_text: Machine Learning thuc lnh vc no?
questions.explanation: Machine Learning l mt nhnh ca Tr tu nhn to, cho php my tnh hc t d liu.

questions.question_text: Supervised Learning s dng d liu c nhn (labeled data).
questions.explanation: Supervised Learning hc t d liu  c gn nhn trc.

questions.question_text: Thut ton no sau y thuc Unsupervised Learning?
questions.explanation: K-Means l thut ton clustering - phn nhm d liu khng c nhn.

questions.question_text: Overfitting xy ra khi m hnh hot ng tt trn training set nhng km trn test set.
questions.explanation: Overfitting l khi m hnh "hc thuc" training data thay v tng qut ha.

questions.question_text: Th vin no dng  x l d liu dng bng trong Python?
questions.explanation: Pandas cung cp DataFrame - cu trc d liu dng bng mnh m.

questions.question_text: NumPy array nhanh hn Python list nh c ti u bng C.
questions.explanation: NumPy s dng C code ti u, nhanh hn 10-100x so vi Python lists.

questions.question_text: Cu lnh no c file CSV trong Pandas?
questions.explanation: pd.read_csv() l hm c file CSV vo DataFrame.

questions.question_text: df.groupby() dng  nhm d liu theo mt ct.
questions.explanation: groupby() cho php aggregate data theo cc nhm.

questions.question_text: Activation function no ph bin nht trong hidden layers ca Deep Learning hin i?
questions.explanation: ReLU (Rectified Linear Unit) gii quyt vanishing gradient v train nhanh hn.

questions.question_text: Backpropagation dng  tnh gradient cho vic cp nht weights.
questions.explanation: Backpropagation tnh o hm ca loss function theo weights bng chain rule.

questions.question_text: Optimizer no kt hp Momentum v RMSprop?
questions.explanation: Adam = Adaptive Moment Estimation, kt hp momentum v adaptive learning rate.

questions.question_text: Dropout l k thut regularization  gim overfitting.
questions.explanation: Dropout randomly "tt" mt s neurons trong training  model robust hn.

questions.question_text: "V" no trong 5Vs  cp n tc  sinh d liu?
questions.explanation: Velocity  cp n tc  data c to ra v cn x l.

questions.question_text: HDFS sao lu d liu trn nhiu nodes  m bo fault tolerance.
questions.explanation: HDFS replication factor mc nh l 3 - mi block lu trn 3 DataNodes.

questions.question_text: Apache Spark nhanh hn MapReduce ch yu nh?
questions.explanation: Spark x l data trong RAM thay v c/ghi disk nh MapReduce.

questions.question_text: Hive cho php query HDFS data bng SQL-like syntax.
questions.explanation: Hive cung cp HiveQL - SQL interface cho Hadoop ecosystem.

questions.question_text: Thnh phn no ca Expert System cha cc IF-THEN rules?
questions.explanation: Knowledge Base lu tr facts v rules ca domain knowledge.

questions.question_text: Forward chaining bt u t goal v tm supporting facts.
questions.explanation: Forward chaining l data-driven, bt u t facts. Backward chaining mi l goal-driven.

questions.question_text: Fuzzy Logic cho php gi tr truth nm trong khong [0,1].
questions.explanation: Khc vi Boolean logic (TRUE/FALSE), Fuzzy logic c degrees of truth.

questions.question_text: Bc cui cng trong Fuzzy Inference System l g?
questions.explanation: Defuzzification chuyn fuzzy output thnh crisp value.

questions.question_text: Qu trnh chia text thnh cc n v nh (words, sentences) gi l g?
questions.explanation: Tokenization chia text thnh tokens (words, subwords, characters).

questions.question_text: Stemming lun cho kt qu l t c ngha trong t in.
questions.explanation: Stemming c th cho kt qu khng phi t tht (vd: "studi" t "studying"). Lemmatization mi m bo t c ngha.

questions.question_text: Word2Vec thuc loi representation no?
questions.explanation: Word2Vec to dense vectors (word embeddings) capture semantic meaning.

questions.question_text: Transformer architecture s dng Self-Attention mechanism.
questions.explanation: "Attention is All You Need" - Transformers da hon ton vo attention, khng dng RNN.

questions.question_text: KDD vit tt ca cm t no?
questions.explanation: KDD - Knowledge Discovery in Databases l quy trnh khai ph tri thc t d liu.

questions.question_text: Association rule {A}  {B} c Support = P(A  B).
questions.explanation: Support o lng tn sut xut hin ca c A v B trong dataset.

questions.question_text: Thut ton no khng cn generate candidate itemsets?
questions.explanation: FP-Growth s dng FP-tree  mine patterns m khng cn candidate generation.

questions.question_text: DBSCAN l thut ton clustering da trn density.
questions.explanation: DBSCAN (Density-Based Spatial Clustering) phn nhm da trn mt  im.
